    "Key": "LivingGrimoire.Orisons.Description",
    "enGB": "Inquisitors can cast a number of {g|Encyclopedia:Cantrips_Orisons}orisons{/g}, or 0-level {g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spells{/g}. These spells are cast like any other spell, but they are not expended when cast and may be used again.",
    "zhCN": "审判官每天可施放若干个祷言，或称0级法术。这些法术的施放方式与其他法术相似，不过在施放后不会被消耗掉，可以再次使用。",
